{"tid":1636992,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"香港第一個五年計劃-良心經濟圈","createTime":"2019-10-08T00:51:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T04:03:45.000Z","uid":4092,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a7273682e3a9f9fd5acb959234f593b956955bda","tid":1636992,"uid":4092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:51:00.000Z","msg":"係依場運動 發唔發現我哋落到街全部都係罷食罷買名單？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">因為港共不斷滲透中資分司壟斷市場</span></span></span> <br />\n<br />\n令到我哋生活離唔開中資<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n係依個第一個五年計劃 我希望能慢慢打造<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黃色</span></span>主導既經濟圈<br />\n<br />\n係無錯 個名係柒咗小小 但的確有要做既需要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n今次運動 我哋曾經比商場 商鋪 黨鐵 連鎖食店 酒店出賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有cctvb發放假新聞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家講抗爭/獨立 港共根本驚都未驚過<br />\n<br />\n但如果日常生活可以罷脱中資 我相信對港共非常不利<br />\n<br />\n係未來五年 我希望不斷有新既良心店鋪出現<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你夠膽係店貼連儂牆 我哋就會大大力懲罰你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但如果係食兩家茶禮哥啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比手足發現咗你會死得仲慘<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">希望大家能夠大大力懲罰良心店鋪</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人 反抗</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"bc675f9cb893f2d4371c47388b3fa9ccc6f788db","tid":1636992,"uid":4092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:51:56.000Z","msg":"屌 紅色大大隻字 寫錯 係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">公司</span>"},{"pid":"852d8cac94ca5699859d8a7a0162e49b9d487646","tid":1636992,"uid":192824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b80b6ad1f562217e8c193a545e1c5169b12dda40","tid":1636992,"uid":272162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:57:53.000Z","msg":"社會主義國家先會用5年計劃"},{"pid":"5af3bd48655325375575b253fb315da3cbe970c6","tid":1636992,"uid":4092,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b80b6ad1f562217e8c193a545e1c5169b12dda40","tid":1636992,"uid":272162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T00:57:53.000Z","msg":"社會主義國家先會用5年計劃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:00:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Then make Hong Kong great again</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e7af3b94f7efb182559fb82875cc013fef662c8","tid":1636992,"uid":22719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T01:10:09.000Z","msg":"我都有諗過呢個問題<br />\n杯葛人地無問題 但一定要搞返個屬於我地既經濟生態"},{"pid":"810ae665e7c9d98df45330c2bd73b1f7e8e3a338","tid":1636992,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T04:03:45.000Z","msg":"請幫手推爆黑警散布謠言, 推到佢四點鐘又口啞啞!!! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" clas